pageProduct.name: SUP ZZZ Sleep 25 Tablets
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Valerian, Passionflower and Magnesium to make your dreams come true.

INVEST IN REST
Work hard. Play hard. Sleep hard. We are in the middle of a sleep revolution and if you aren't already on board, get ready. There is compelling evidence revealing the power of sleep for just about every human function. However, with our busy, modern lifestyles, it's hard to find enough time to recharge.

WHY POP SUP?
This calming blend of herbs and Magnesium is raising the bar for sleep. There is a long history of traditional use in Western herbal medicine that shows the ability of Valerian to improve sleep quality, reduce time taken to fall asleep and reduce those mid-sleep stirs. SUP helps:

- Support your restful sleep and help relieve nervous tension
- Reduce stress for a more peaceful mind
- Increase sleep quality and deep sleep
- Calm and relax your mind, body and soul POPSUP

Size: 25 Tablets

KEY FEATURES

• Support your restful sleep and help relieve nervous tension
• Reduce stress for a more peaceful mind
• Increase sleep quality and deep sleep
• Calm and relax your mind, body and soul
• Vegan Friendly

Warnings

If symptoms persist talk to your health professional. Mineral supplements should not replace a balanced diet. Do not use if tamper evident seal is broken or missing.

Ingredients

Passiflora incarnata (Passionflower) flower ext. dry conc. 200mg
Equiv. to (Passiflora incarnata) flower dry 1000mg
Magnesium phosphate tribasic 108.15mg
Equiv. to Elemental magnesium 30mg
Valeriana officinalis (Valerian) root ext. dry conc. 150mg
Equiv. to (Valeriana officinalis) root dry 750mg
Humulus lupulus (Hops) fruit ext. dry conc. 16.67mg
Equiv. to (Humulus lupulus) fruit dry 125mg
Melissa officinalis (Lemon balm) herb ext. dry conc. 12.5mg
Equiv. to (Melissa officinalis) herb dry 125mg

Directions

Adults only
POP 1-2 tablets one hour before sleep.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25oC
